      "subject": "This week at The Quarry — Apr 28–May 4",
      "htmlBody": "<div style=\"background:#f4f5f7;padding:2rem 1rem;font-family:'Montserrat',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;color:#1c1f26;line-height:1.6;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem 1.5rem;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\">\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:2px solid #9a7b2a;\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;\">\n    <img src=\"https://thequarrystl.com/assets/icons/icon-512.png\" alt=\"The Quarry\" width=\"72\" height=\"72\" style=\"display:block;margin:0 auto 0.5rem;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;\">\n  </a>\n  <div style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.4rem;color:#1c1f26;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">THE QUARRY</div>\n  <div style=\"font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:0.7rem;color:#858d9e;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0.25rem;\">Wine &middot; Bites &middot; Live Music &middot; Golf</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;font-family:Georgia,serif;color:#2c2c2c;background:#ffffff;padding:32px 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9a7b2a;margin:0 0 8px\">Week of April 28, 2026</p>\n  <h1 style=\"font-size:26px;font-weight:normal;margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.3\">This Week at The Quarry</h1>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 24px\">A quieter week on the calendar — which means more room to settle in, eat well, and let the evening stretch out.</p>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #e8e0d0;margin:0 0 24px\">\n\n  <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse\">\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0ebe1;vertical-align:top\">\n        <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 4px\">Live Music</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#555;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.5\">We keep the stage warm all week. Check this week's lineup and set times before you head out.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:underline\">See who's playing →</a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:14px 0;vertical-align:top\">\n        <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 4px\">Dinner Any Night</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#555;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.5\">The kitchen is open, the patio is ready, and walk-ins are always welcome — though a reservation never hurts.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/reservations?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:underline\">Reserve your table →</a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <div style=\"margin:32px 0 0;text-align:center\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#9a7b2a;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:15px;padding:14px 32px;letter-spacing:0.04em\">See What's Coming Up</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#555;margin:40px 0 0;line-height:1.6\">We'll see you at the table.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2c2c2c;margin:6px 0 0;font-weight:bold\">The Quarry Team</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:2rem auto 0;padding:1.5rem 1rem;border-top:1px solid #e0e3e8;font-family:'Montserrat',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;color:#858d9e;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:0.85rem;\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;margin:0 0.6rem;display:inline-block;\" title=\"thequarrystl.com\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:18px;height:18px;vertical-align:middle;line-height:0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#9a7b2a\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"/><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"/></svg></span></a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;margin:0 0.6rem;display:inline-block;\" title=\"Facebook\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:18px;height:18px;vertical-align:middle;line-height:0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#9a7b2a\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\"><path d=\"M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z\"/></svg></span></a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;margin:0 0.6rem;display:inline-block;\" title=\"Instagram\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:18px;height:18px;vertical-align:middle;line-height:0;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#9a7b2a\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" rx=\"5\" ry=\"5\"/><path d=\"M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z\"/><line x1=\"17.5\" y1=\"6.5\" x2=\"17.51\" y2=\"6.5\"/></svg></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\n    <strong style=\"color:#4b5263;\">The Quarry</strong> &middot; 3960 Highway Z, New Melle, MO 63385 &middot; (636) 224-8257\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">thequarrystl.com</a> &middot;\n    <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">facebook.com/thequarrystl</a> &middot;\n    <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">@thequarrystl</a>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n    You're receiving this because you signed up, booked a reservation, or attended an event at The Quarry.\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/.netlify/functions/unsubscribe?email={email}\" style=\"color:#858d9e;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "innerHtml": "<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;font-family:Georgia,serif;color:#2c2c2c;background:#ffffff;padding:32px 24px\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9a7b2a;margin:0 0 8px\">Week of April 28, 2026</p>\n  <h1 style=\"font-size:26px;font-weight:normal;margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.3\">This Week at The Quarry</h1>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 24px\">A quieter week on the calendar — which means more room to settle in, eat well, and let the evening stretch out.</p>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #e8e0d0;margin:0 0 24px\">\n\n  <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse\">\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0ebe1;vertical-align:top\">\n        <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 4px\">Live Music</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#555;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.5\">We keep the stage warm all week. Check this week's lineup and set times before you head out.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:underline\">See who's playing →</a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:14px 0;vertical-align:top\">\n        <p style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 4px\">Dinner Any Night</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#555;margin:0 0 6px;line-height:1.5\">The kitchen is open, the patio is ready, and walk-ins are always welcome — though a reservation never hurts.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/reservations?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:underline\">Reserve your table →</a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <div style=\"margin:32px 0 0;text-align:center\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events?utm_source=email&utm_medium=marketing&utm_campaign=weekly_digest\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#9a7b2a;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:15px;padding:14px 32px;letter-spacing:0.04em\">See What's Coming Up</a>\n  </div>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#555;margin:40px 0 0;line-height:1.6\">We'll see you at the table.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#2c2c2c;margin:6px 0 0;font-weight:bold\">The Quarry Team</p>\n</div>",
